description: Fabelio is a furniture brand that combines the richness of Indonesia’s design and craftsmanship, while adding a modern touch to it at 20-30% cheaper price than competition.

Factorial is a SaaS platform that streamlines HR workflows, from payroll to talent management, lowering costs, reducing low value-added manual tasks, and creating useful insights for SME decision makers.

Family Corporation carries both people and goods through three main divisions: Family Transport, Family Cargo and Family Car Rental. It offers customized routes and schedules, automated fleet and revenue management systems, and in-house maintenance centers.
FashionValet is Malaysia’s first multi-label fashion company that provides women and men access to the best Southeast Asian designers and designs through its website and retail stores.
Fastmind helps large enterprises improve their digital conversion rate by up to 3X by creating a personalized post ad click experience for every user.
Fatture in Cloud (FIC) provides Italian SME owners with cloud-based software to seamlessly issue e-invoices and manage their businesses under the new regulatory standards.
Female Daily Network helps Indonesian women look and feel beautiful and is the largest online community for young Indonesian women.
Fën Hoteles offers comprehensive franchise and hotel management services.

Driven by the passion to transform tiles from just wall and floor coverings into a lifestyle element for any space, Feruni Ceramiche is one of the leading brands in upmarket ceramic and porcelain tiles.
Field Agent provides physical retailers and consumer packaged goods (CPG) brands with data analytics to get consumer insights and inform product trials.
Field Intelligence is a technology-enabled pharmaceutical distributor that provides retail pharmacies with access to data-driven planning, fulfillment, quality medication and inventory financing.
Figopara is a supplier financing platform formed to expand the circulating capital that companies need.
FIGS is seeking to revolutionize the medical apparel industry through its line of tailored and technical scrubs sold direct to consumer. FIGS IPO’d on the NYSE in May 2021.
FilmHouse and FilmOne provide platforms to support the thriving Nigerian film industry (Nollywood).

FinConecta is an enterprise software company driving the digitization of the financial services industry with its proprietary middleware platform, 4wrd, which connects financial institutions to fintechs via standardized API integration.
Finsocial provides personal and payroll loans to teachers and pensioners through a fully digital system that can analyze a customer’s credit-worthiness in minutes and disburse funds within a day.

First Circle is an online financing platform designed to provide short-term loans to small and medium enterprises in the Philippines. After First Circle, Tony founded EditMode, a software solution that makes it easier to manage and change content on the web.
First-Class Mining Attachments (FMA) designs and manufactures auxiliary equipment and special attachments that increase safety and productivity in mines.
Fleetio is a SaaS platform that helps companies track and optimize their fleets in real-time.
FlexClub is an all-inclusive vehicle subscription platform for business and consumers.
